(4254, 1064, 'value_hero_quote', 'Whether you are seeking the acquisition or sale of a special interest auto we approach each transaction diligently with the following in mind:'),
(4255, 1064, '_value_hero_quote', 'field_591bb5add388e'),
(4256, 1064, 'value_hero_image', '164'),
(4257, 1064, '_value_hero_image', 'field_591bb5d7d388f'),
(4258, 1064, 'value', '4'),
(4259, 1064, '_value', 'field_591bb613d3890'),
(4260, 1064, 'value_title_1', 'Market Analysis'),
(4261, 1064, '_value_title_1', 'field_591bb62ed3891'),
(4262, 1064, 'value_body_1', 'As with any investment, market conditions and their prospective outcome can easily decide a good investment from a bad one. We have an in-depth understanding of market fluctuation in the collector car hobby, so much in fact it is applied to every buying or selling situation that we facilitate. From this our clients take away a solid investment that they can enjoy for years to come, and when the appropriate opportunity to sell presents itself he/she will yield adequate returns.'),
(4263, 1064, '_value_body_1', 'field_591bb655e95da'),
(4264, 1064, 'value_title_4', 'Full Service Process'),
(4265, 1064, '_value_title_4', 'field_591bb6b7e95df'),
(4266, 1064, 'value_body_4', 'LBI makes it a point to provide a hassle free process; where by initial investigation, pre-purchase inspection, negotiations, related paperwork, transfer of monies, logistics, and post purchase car care are all performed by LBI. This ensures there is consistency and efficiency in the transaction and ultimately our clients total satisfaction.'),
(4267, 1064, '_value_body_4', 'field_591bb6cbe95e0'),
(4268, 1064, 'value_title_2', 'Honesty'),
(4269, 1064, '_value_title_2', 'field_591bb678e95db'),
(4270, 1064, 'value_body_2', 'LBI emphasizes it\'s dedication to being the buyers advocate. As the new generation of Brokers in an effort to benchmark service without cutting corners LBI has made it a promise to our clients to fully evaluate all aspects of every transaction. Ensuring we provide what you expect in purchasing a collector car or any other luxury item.'),
(4271, 1064, '_value_body_2', 'field_591bb688e95dc'),
(4272, 1064, 'value_title_3', 'Protection of Financial Interest'),
(4273, 1064, '_value_title_3', 'field_591bb698e95dd'),
(4274, 1064, 'value_body_3', 'Monetary protection becomes paramount in any transaction no matter the item. Your financial interest is maintained through our due-diligence and protected by handling any and all funds through a secure means, while always keeping you up to date on the transaction.'),
