(19957, 2, '2013-10-07 13:37:42', '2013-10-07 13:37:42', 'Calling all car collectors, parts sellers, and enthusiasts!  Its fall and that means the annual  AACA Fall Meet is upon us where people from across the globe visit historic Hershey Park. The auto pilgrimage is happening this week starting Wednesday, October 9<sup>th</sup> through Saturday October 12<sup>th</sup>. During this time, the car corral will have a wide variety of cars for sale in which anyone can choose from. In the flea Market, onlookers can browse through what seems like endless amounts of car parts, accessories, and junk. The four day event ends with a great show on Saturday the 12<sup>th</sup>. Take a look at the following link for event schedule: http://www.hersheyaaca.org/fm_schedule.html\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHershey is an excellent opportunity to mingle with other car-guys, look at some great cars, and purchase whatever you need for the next project.  If you haven’t attended this event, it is a must do for any car enthusiast. LBI will be there all four days so contact us! We will have about 6 cars in the corral and flea market. Below are some of our cars that you will be able to see in person if you attend the event. Enjoy!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://www.lbilimited.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/63-190SL18.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-19958" alt="63 190SL18" src="http://www.lbilimited.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/63-190SL18-300x199.jpg" width="300" height="199" /></a><a href="http://www.lbilimited.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/55-17.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-19959" alt="55 17" src="http://www.lbilimited.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/55-17-300x199.jpg" width="300" height="199" /></a><a href="http://www.lbilimited.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/DSC_1184.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-19960" alt="DSC_1184" src="http://www.lbilimited.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/DSC_1184-300x199.jpg" width="300" height="199" /></a>', 'AACA Fall Meet at 